body:
Heyo, 
So I've been here on Avicus for 3 years. I first joined on December 16th 2013. I met a lot of new people and really enjoyed the server so I decided to stay. 2 years later on December 30th 2015 I was promoted to Junior Mod and 3 weeks later on January 20th or something like that I was promoted to full mod and I still am to this day. I've met a lot of new people throughout those 3 years, some have stayed, some have gone but I am still meeting new people everyday and that's why I love this server and that's why I am still here to this very day!
So ask me anything! 
#TargetCammy
#NiceMeme
#AntiKnockbackAussies
Also {tag=0af038412894434ca4be965b317244e8} told me to add this
